Subject: Re: [T2] CV Joint Swap

As long as both buses are stick shifts the entire axles will swap.

However, I've found that age is not a great predictor of CV joint life.
If they've gone this long, they're likely to last a good deal longer.  I
wouldn't go to the trouble of changing them out until the boots have a
problem!

George

